  "description": {
   "en": "Rannosuke Hanayagi, the 17th heir to the Kurokami House, runs a business of vice and cruelty under the guise of a renowned ikebana school across the country. He consumes the girls like cigarettes, tortures them and humiliates them at leisure. Through his links with the economic and political world, which he holds firmly by giving him the benefit of his sexual slaves, Rannosuke is an untouchable sadist prince who reigns over an empire of lust. He is embarking on the education of a new girl, Sayuri, who is to become the new queen of this empire. She becomes the ultimate object of the master's desire"
